Description: A comprehensive styling system for consistent visual outputs using CSIDS guidelines. 
    Provides ggplot2 themes, color palettes, and dual formatting functions to standardize 
    graphs, tables, and reports. Includes Norwegian formatting conventions for domestic 
    use and international journal standards for academic publications. Features number 
    formatting (percentages, per-100k rates, log transformations), date formatting 
    (Norwegian vs ISO 8601), and a hierarchical color system. Focuses on consistency 
    over flexibility to ensure reproducible, professional outputs across research contexts.
